fn.p:
We have revised the manuscript in line with reviewer comments provided through our eLife submission. Specifically, we have made the following revisions:
- Clarification of surrogate analysis;
- Clarification of linear mixed-effects models;
- Provide channel-specific relationships between coherence and apnoea rate (Figure S4);
- Clarification of rationale and research question;
- Clarification of figure captions for Figures 2 and 3;
- Provided a more cautious interpretation of the directionality analysis;
- Summarised Apgar score differently;
- Described the confounding effects of sleep and caffeine (Figure S6);
- Added a note on our limited spatial resolution.
